Accessibility of starting point: Cable railway / cable car
Finishing point: Grindelwald (1,034)
Altitude difference: 1,196 metres

Level of difficulty: medium
Toboggan hire onsite: yes
Illuminated for night sledging: no
Option to eat: at the start and at the finish
